This is a Python-based Library Management System built for a school using:

- Tkinter for the Graphical User Interface (GUI)
- MySQL as the backend database
- Pillow for image support in the GUI

The system allows you to manage books, track student members, and perform core library operations â€” all through a simple, user-friendly interface.

ðŸŽ¯ Features

âœ… Register new student members using their **Roll Number** and **Name**  
âœ… Add books with multiple copies (based on **Book Title**, **Author**)  
âœ… Automatically increment book copy count if the same book is added again  
âœ… Issue books to registered students (copies are decremented)  
âœ… Return books and update the number of available copies  
âœ… Delete books by **Book ID**  
âœ… Attractive front page with background image and stylized welcome message  


